HOW TO SET UP WIRELESS ADB FOR FTC PHONES

A Robot Controller IP Address: 192.168.1.99
B Robot Controller IP Address: 192.168.1.100


CONNECTION:

Plug in phone

In terminal, type>

    adb tcpip 5555

Then type>

    adb connect <PHONE IP ADDRESS>:5555

Unplug phone, adb is connected wirelessly.


DISCONNECTION

In terminal, type>

    adb disconnect <PHONE IP ADDRESS>

Phone no longer connected wirelessly.


TO CHECK FOR ADB DEVICES THAT ARE CONNECTED

In terminal, type>

    adb devices

A list of the device IP's will show up.